---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - GoPropReels Deal Finder">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Last updated: December 4, 2025</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
        GoPropReels Deal Finder ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. 
        This Privacy Policy explains how our Chrome Extension handles your information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Data Collection</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
        <strong>We do not collect, store, or sell your personal data.</strong>
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
        The GoPropReels Deal Finder extension operates locally on your device. It checks the URL of the website you are visiting 
        solely to determine if a relevant coupon code is available for that specific domain. This check happens instantly 
        and no browsing history is transmitted to our servers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. External Connections</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
        The extension periodically connects to our server (<code>https://gopropreels.com</code>) to fetch the latest list of 
        deals and coupons (a JSON file). This process does not transmit any user-identifiable information.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
        This extension uses affiliate links. When you click on a coupon or deal button within the extension, 
        you may be redirected through an affiliate link. This means we may earn a commission if you make a purchase, 
        at no additional cost to you.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">5. Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: 
        <a href="mailto:goreelsteam@gmail.com" class="text-brand-accent hover:underline">goreelsteam@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
